ntence\": \"Unlike some of those projects, however, \\\"Sprint\\\" was partially born out of the desire to construct a narrative modeled around brevity.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those projects\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Sprint\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1187}, {\"ngram\": \"the desire\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"a narrative\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"brevity\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the elite level for both men and women, short sprints like the 100 and 200 rarely exceed more than 10 to 20 seconds per race.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the elite level\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"both men\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1306}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"short sprints\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 10 to 20 seconds\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Related Perhaps equally as difficult as defining the scope of a short-lived competition through film is capturing the \\\"emotional journey\\\" that preceded it, as Martin tells Salon during a recent interview.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1565, \"end\": 1571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9602724345768431, \"rank\": 0.03532468376978367, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}, {\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"score\": 0.9999996926255125, \"rank\": 3.0653312409109335e-07, \"text\": \"Salon\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r