tes between, the semifinal and the final when she goes back to the warm-up track and she meets Dennis [Mitchell], her coach.\", \"from\": 5210, \"to\": 5360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only 20 minutes\", \"from\": 5224, \"to\": 5239}, {\"ngram\": \"the warm-up track\", \"from\": 5299, \"to\": 5316}, {\"ngram\": \"Dennis\", \"from\": 5331, \"to\": 5337}, {\"ngram\": \"[Mitchell\", \"from\": 5338, \"to\": 5347}, {\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 5350, \"to\": 5359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And they are both incredibly interesting but complicated characters.\", \"from\": 5361, \"to\": 5429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"incredibly interesting but complicated characters\", \"from\": 5379, \"to\": 5428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dennis and Sha'Carri - they are both characters that people have very strong opinions about, for good and for bad.\", \"from\": 5430, \"to\": 5544, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dennis\", \"from\": 5430, \"to\": 5436}, {\"ngram\": \"characters\", \"from\": 5467, \"to\": 5477}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5483, \"to\": 5489}, {\"ngram\": \"very strong opinions\", \"from\": 5495, \"to\": 5515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think in that moment, the way that Dennis talks to her between the events .\", \"from\": 5545, \"to\": 5626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 5560, \"to\": 5571}, {\"ngram\": \"Dennis\", \"from\": 5586, \"to\": 5592}, {\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 5614, \"to\": 5624}]}, {\"sentence\": \".\", \"from\": 5627, \"to\": 5628, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \".\", \"from\": 5629, \"to\": 5630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"and it's this great moment of him holding her hands as they walk from the warm-up track to send her out to the final.\", \"from\": 5631, \"to\": 5748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this great moment\", \"from\": 5640, \"to\": 5657}, {\"ngram\": \"her hands\", \"from\": 5673, \"to\": 5682}, {\"ngram\": \"the warm-up track\", \"from\": 5701, \"to\": 5718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he stops and they hug and he whispers something to her like, \\\"Listen, I am going to ask you this question and I want you to tell me the answer.\", \"from\": 5749, \"to\": 5896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5791, \"to\": 5800}, {\"ngram\": \"this question\", \"from\": 5845, \"to\": 5858}, {\"ngram\": \"the answer\", \"from\": 5885, \"to\": 5895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just want you to go out there and show me.\\\"\", \"from\": 5897, \"to\": 5942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that question is, \\\"Who's the fastest?\\\"\", \"from\": 5943, \"to\": 5985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that question\", \"from\": 5947, \"to\": 5960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then she goes out there and she just produces the most extraordinary performance to win the gold medal.\", \"from\": 5987, \"to\": 6094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most extraordinary performance\", \"from\": 6037, \"to\": 6071}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 6079, \"to\": 6093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then in the aftermath, because he's separated from her, he's on the phone with his wife.\", \"from\": 6095, \"to\": 6187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the aftermath\", \"from\": 6107, \"to\": 6120}, {\"ngram\": \"the phone\", \"from\": 6163, \"to\": 6172}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 6178, \"to\": 6186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The whole thing is, it's just what sports are all about.\", \"from\": 6188, \"to\": 6244, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The whole thing\", \"from\": 6188, \"to\": 6203}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 6223, \"to\": 6229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are two people that have been criticized and maligned, all the stuff that's been written about Sha'Carri and even Dennis.\", \"from\": 6245, \"to\": 6371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two people\", \"from\": 6254, \"to\": 6264}, {\"ngram\": \"all the stuff\", \"from\": 6305, \"to\": 6318}, {\"ngram\": \"Sha'Carri\", \"from\": 6345, \"to\": 6354}, {\"ngram\": \"even Dennis\", \"from\": 6359, \"to\": 6370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And here you just see it for that moment of winning gold medals.\", \"from\": 6372, \"to\": 6436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 6401, \"to\": 6412}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medals\", \"from\": 6424, \"to\": 6435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You just see how it affects them on a human level.\", \"from\": 6437, \"to\": 6487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a human level\", \"from\": 6473, \"to\": 6486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's just incredibly emotional, incredibly powerful.\", \"from\": 6488, \"to\": 6548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, it just epitomizes everything that's wonderful about every sport, but certainly about that sport.\", \"from\": 6549, \"to\": 6654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 6576, \"to\": 6586}, {\"ngram\": \"every sport\", \"from\": 6610, \"to\": 6621}, {\"ngram\": \"that sport\", \"from\": 6643, \"to\": 6653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I never tire of watching it.\", \"from\": 6655, \"to\": 6687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It just really makes me emotional every time I see it because I think you really understand the hard work that each of them have put in to get into that moment and being able to execute and get what they dreamed of, which is incredible.\", \"from\": 6688, \"to\": 6924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hard work\", \"from\": 6780, \"to\": 6793}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 6836, \"to\": 6847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Totally.\", \"from\": 6926, \"to\": 6934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was actually going to ask something along those lines, regarding Sha'Carri specifically.\", \"from\": 6935, \"to\": 7025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 6963, \"to\": 6972}, {\"ngram\": \"those lines\", \"from\": 6979, \"to\": 6990}, {\"ngram\": \"Sha'Carri\", \"from\": 7002, \"to\": 7011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When she wins the 100 meters at The World Championships in Budapest, it really feels not only like a culmination of her efforts, but the moment when no one can count her out anymore.\", \"from\": 7026, \"to\": 7208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7085, \"end\": 7093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999118784016523, \"rank\": 3.657947791461551e-05, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 100 meters\", \"from\": 7040, \"to\": 7054}, {\"ngram\": \"The World Championships\", \"from\": 7058, \"to\": 7081}, {\"ngram\": \"a culmination\", \"from\": 7125, \"to\": 7138}, {\"ngram\": \"her efforts\", \"from\": 7142, \"to\": 7153}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 7159, \"to\": 7169}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 7175, \"to\": 7181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It affected me emotionally - that moment when she and Dennis embrace after the race and he gets kind of choked up and he reminds her of all she deserves.\", \"from\": 7209, \"to\": 7362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dennis\", \"from\": 7263, \"to\": 7269}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 7284, \"to\": 7292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After Sha'Carri's unfortunatesuspensionin 2021 that led her to not be able to participate in the Tokyo Olympics, what did it mean to be a part of that moment for her and with her, that 100-meter win where she set that record?\", \"from\": 7364, \"to\": 7590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 7457, \"to\": 7475}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 7500, \"to\": 7506}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 7510, \"to\": 7521}, {\"ngram\": \"that record\", \"from\": 7577, \"to\": 7588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those moments are just incredible to witness.\", \"from\": 7592, \"to\": 7637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those moments\", \"from\": 7592, \"to\": 7605}, {\"ngram\": \"witness\", \"from\": 7629, \"to\": 7636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think for our crew, it was that she is an incredibly complicated individual to carry.\", \"from\": 7638, \"to\": 7729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our crew\", \"from\": 7654, \"to\": 7662}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredibly complicated individual\", \"from\": 7683, \"to\": 7719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And still, though we have made this series about her - I would not claim to have any grasp on who she really is and what really drives her.\", \"from\": 7730, \"to\": 7869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this series\", \"from\": 7761, \"to\": 7772}, {\"ngram\": \"any grasp\", \"from\": 7811, \"to\": 7820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think that she was thoroughly deserving of that gold medal and thoroughly deserving of everything that she got.\", \"from\": 7871, \"to\": 7988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that gold medal\", \"from\": 7920, \"to\": 7935}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 7964, \"to\": 7974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And thoroughly deserving of, like you said, that ability to not have people that do not know anything about her question her anymore, because I think there was a lot of rubbish written about her and talked about her both before and after what kind of happened to her.\", \"from\": 7989, \"to\": 8256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that ability\", \"from\": 8033, \"to\": 8045}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 8058, \"to\": 8064}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 8082, \"to\": 8090}, {\"ngram\": \