m\": 13763, \"to\": 13771}, {\"ngram\": \"the mom\", \"from\": 13775, \"to\": 13782}, {\"ngram\": \"Dennis\", \"from\": 13786, \"to\": 13792}, {\"ngram\": \"a father figure\", \"from\": 13822, \"to\": 13837}, {\"ngram\": \"kind of Sha'Carri\", \"from\": 13841, \"to\": 13858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I think it's it's really important to establish those relationships and those characters within the context of the series so that you can see that the emotional states do not just lie with the individual.\", \"from\": 13860, \"to\": 14067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those relationships\", \"from\": 13911, \"to\": 13930}, {\"ngram\": \"those characters\", \"from\": 13935, \"to\": 13951}, {\"ngram\": \"the context\", \"from\": 13959, \"to\": 13970}, {\"ngram\": \"the series\", \"from\": 13974, \"to\": 13984}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotional states\", \"from\": 14010, \"to\": 14030}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual\", \"from\": 14052, \"to\": 14066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They lie with the bigger team and they lie with the mom, the parent, the brother, whatever it is.\", \"from\": 14068, \"to\": 14165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bigger team\", \"from\": 14082, \"to\": 14097}, {\"ngram\": \"the mom\", \"from\": 14116, \"to\": 14123}, {\"ngram\": \"the parent\", \"from\": 14125, \"to\": 14135}, {\"ngram\": \"the brother\", \"from\": 14137, \"to\": 14148}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 14150, \"to\": 14158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think it's always an important part of these worlds to see.\", \"from\": 14166, \"to\": 14231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an important part\", \"from\": 14190, \"to\": 14207}, {\"ngram\": \"these worlds\", \"from\": 14211, \"to\": 14223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Americans do not like people who do not win.\\\"\", \"from\": 14233, \"to\": 14279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Americans\", \"from\": 14234, \"to\": 14243}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 14256, \"to\": 14262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, I spoke to my own mom on my way into the office today.\", \"from\": 14281, \"to\": 14343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my own mom\", \"from\": 14300, \"to\": 14310}, {\"ngram\": \"my way\", \"from\": 14314, \"to\": 14320}, {\"ngram\": \"the office\", \"from\": 14326, \"to\": 14336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I live in L.A., she lives in the U.K. and I was on the phone to her and she was like, \\\"I just watched your 'Sprint' show and I loved Noah's mom!\", \"from\": 14344, \"to\": 14488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14354, \"end\": 14358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L.A._Reid\", \"score\": 0.9977509861573283, \"rank\": 0.0022532178803332963, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L.A._Reid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L.A._Reid\"}, {\"begin\": 14377, \"end\": 14381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999800697480615, \"rank\": 1.0797652666050054e-05, \"text\": \"U.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 14477, \"end\": 14481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder_and_Noah_Mayer\", \"score\": 0.9989907242444349, \"rank\": 0.0010050113530708704, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder_and_Noah_Mayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder_and_Noah_Mayer\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the phone\", \"from\": 14395, \"to\": 14404}, {\"ngram\": \"your 'Sprint' show\", \"from\": 14446, \"to\": 14464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was great.\", \"from\": 14489, \"to\": 14503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was pulling out all the baby photos and stuff like that.\\\"\", \"from\": 14504, \"to\": 14565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngra