"from\": 14965, \"to\": 14976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in the U.S., that's not exactly the case.\", \"from\": 14978, \"to\": 15023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 14985, \"to\": 14993}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 15014, \"to\": 15022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Track and field is certainly not as popular as bigger team sports like football and basketball, for example.\", \"from\": 15024, \"to\": 15132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Track\", \"from\": 15024, \"to\": 15029}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 15034, \"to\": 15039}, {\"ngram\": \"bigger team sports\", \"from\": 15071, \"to\": 15089}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 15095, \"to\": 15103}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 15108, \"to\": 15118}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 15124, \"to\": 15131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How much did you want to show the contrast between how sprinters are publicly perceived and understood in Jamaica versus the U.S.?\", \"from\": 15133, \"to\": 15263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15239, \"end\": 15246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9995083141808598, \"rank\": 0.00045096087153237457, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the contrast\", \"from\": 15163, \"to\": 15175}, {\"ngram\": \"sprinters\", \"from\": 15188, \"to\": 15197}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 15254, \"to\": 15262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it was an important part of the the narrative, and it was an important part of establishing the characters and the additional pressures that they are faced with in Jamaica.\", \"from\": 15265, \"to\": 15445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15437, \"end\": 15444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9995083141808598, \"rank\": 0.00045096087153237457, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an important part\", \"from\": 15280, \"to\": 15297}, {\"ngram\": \"the the narrative\", \"from\": 15301, \"to\": 15318}, {\"ngram\": \"an important part\", \"from\": 15331, \"to\": 15348}, {\"ngram\": \"the characters\", \"from\": 15365, \"to\": 15379}, {\"ngram\": \"the additional pressures\", \"from\": 15384, \"to\": 15408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Michael Johnson says in his commentary on it, \\\"In Jamaica, if you do not win the gold, they are really not interested in silver.\\\"\", \"from\": 15446, \"to\": 15575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15446, \"end\": 15461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.656240695637341, \"rank\": 0.27532889874352734, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\"}, {\"begin\": 15496, \"end\": 15503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9995083141808598, \"rank\": 0.00045096087153237457, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his commentary\", \"from\": 15470, \"to\": 15484}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 15523, \"to\": 15531}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 15567, \"to\": 15573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And sprinting has become so synonymous with Jamaica.\", \"from\": 15576, \"to\": 15628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15620, \"end\": 15627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9995083141808598, \"rank\": 0.00045096087153237457, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sprinting\", \"from\": 15580, \"to\": 15589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It gives them a cultural identity above and beyond music and stuff like that.\", \"from\": 15629, \"to\": 15706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cultural identity\", \"from\": 15643, \"to\": 15662}, {\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 15680, \"to\": 15685}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 15690, \"to\": 15695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think that that's important for a tiny island like Jamaica.\", \"from\": 15707, \"to\": 15772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15764, \"end\": 15771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9995083141808598, \"rank\": 0.00045096087153237457, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tiny island\", \"from\": 15745, \"to\": 15758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the U.S., it is different.\", \"from\": 15774, \"to\": 15803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 15777, \"to\": 15785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Track and field is competing with a lot of other sports.\", \"from\": 15804, \"to\": 15860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Track\", \"from\": 15804, \"to\": 15809}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 15814, \"to\": 15819}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 15838, \"to\": 15843}, {\"ngram\": \"other sports\", \"from\": 15847, \"to\": 15859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think that for me, the 100 meters is such a blue ribbon event in any sport.\", \"from\": 15861, \"to\": 15942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 100 meters\", \"from\": 15886, \"to\": 15900}, {\"ngram\": \"such a blue ribbon event\", \"from\": 15904, \"to\": 15928}, {\"ngram\": \"any sport\", \"from\": 15932, \"to\": 15941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it would be interesting to see if Noah does win Olympic gold in the 100 