ssive fan\", \"from\": 18083, \"to\": 18096}, {\"ngram\": \"a runner\", \"from\": 18107, \"to\": 18115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a massive fan of him.\", \"from\": 18117, \"to\": 18143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a massive fan\", \"from\": 18122, \"to\": 18135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So to have him in the show was probably a personal dream come true for me to have it.\", \"from\": 18144, \"to\": 18229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 18162, \"to\": 18170}, {\"ngram\": \"a personal dream\", \"from\": 18184, \"to\": 18200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think Allyson, you know, brought another level.\", \"from\": 18230, \"to\": 18283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18242, \"end\": 18249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allyson_Maynard_Gibson\", \"score\": 0.9999686980925545, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Allyson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allyson_Maynard_Gibson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allyson_Maynard_Gibson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another level\", \"from\": 18269, \"to\": 18282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Ato - Ato was someone that, you know, it was a really big personality.\", \"from\": 18284, \"to\": 18358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ato - Ato\", \"from\": 18288, \"to\": 18297}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 18302, \"to\": 18309}, {\"ngram\": \"a really big personality\", \"from\": 18333, \"to\": 18357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Right, yes, Ato Boldon.\", \"from\": 18360, \"to\": 18383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18372, \"end\": 18382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ato_Boldon\", \"score\": 0.9999055817777021, \"rank\": 9.442713792255189e-05, \"text\": \"Ato Boldon\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ato_Boldon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ato_Boldon\"}], \"noun_phrase