\": 18919}, {\"ngram\": \"reasons\", \"from\": 18923, \"to\": 18930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it really wasn't difficult to get people on board a show like this because they could all see the potential benefit of being on a platform like Netflix and the global audience that always brings.\", \"from\": 18932, \"to\": 19130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19079, \"end\": 19086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 0.9999249894255201, \"rank\": 7.434898773612369e-05, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 18969, \"to\": 18975}, {\"ngram\": \"board\", \"from\": 18979, \"to\": 18984}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential benefit\", \"from\": 19029, \"to\": 19050}, {\"ngram\": \"a platform\", \"from\": 19063, \"to\": 19073}, {\"ngram\": \"the global audience\", \"from\": 19091, \"to\": 19110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, yeah, it was it was a perfect storm to be able to get, those names involved in the show.\", \"from\": 19131, \"to\": 19223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a perfect storm\", \"from\": 19155, \"to\": 19170}, {\"ngram\": \"those names\", \"from\": 19190, \"to\": 19201}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 19214, \"to\": 19222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are following the same group of athletes featured in \\\"Sprint\\\" to Paris this summer, which is really exciting.\", \"from\": 19225, \"to\": 19338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19294, \"end\": 19299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9998602999628147, \"rank\": 0.00013971955159721315, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same group\", \"from\": 19243, \"to\": 19257}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 19261, \"to\": 19269}, {\"ngram\": \"\